            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Finland tops the rankings with a score of 7.76, continuing its streak as the world's happiest country</li>\n<li>Nordic countries dominate the top 5, all scoring above 7.2</li>\n<li>Afghanistan scores lowest at around 1.7, reflecting decades of conflict and instability</li>\n<li>Costa Rica scores 7.44, the highest among non-European nations and higher than many wealthy countries</li>\n</ul></span>"
